:: Intro [nobr] {"position":"1136,19","size":"100,100"}
<<SetSpeaker "Sunken Motor Carriage">>
<<AddParagraph "The ice crunches and squeels under your feet as you and Kim approach the wreck of your Coupris Mark 40, a break in the case load having given you the chance to pay your overdue respects.">>

<<AddParagraph "The motor carriage has changed remarkably little since last time you saw it, and while it's objectively depressing to see its rusting hull, there's a nostalgia in being here again and being able to mark the progress in your life past this point.">>

<<SetSpeaker "Kim Kitsuragi">>
<<AddParagraph "Kim also seems caught up in thought, looking out over the sea and absentmindedly adjusting his bomber jacket as you are both caressed by the cool wind coming in off the coast.">>

<<SetSpeaker "Kim Kitsuragi">>
<<AddParagraph "He comes to his senses first, noticing you staring and giving one of his small smiles. \"Well, let's get to it then,\" he remarks, pulling a small plastic bottle out of his jacket.">>

<<PassiveSkill "Electrochemistry">>
<<AddParagraph "Ooooooh what do we have here???!! Looks DRINKABLE Harry-boy!">>

<<AddOption "What's that?" "StartFuneral">>[[|StartFuneral]]


:: StartFuneral [nobr] {"position":"959,8","size":"100,100"}
<<PassiveSkill "Encyclopedia" "Easy" "Success">>
<<AddParagraph "Libation, pouring out a last drink for the departed. What type of liquor varies from region to region but the sentiment is always the same. The lieutenant appears to have gone with something cheap.">>

<<PassiveSkill "esprit De Corps" "Moderate" "Success">>
<<AddParagraph "A tradition of its own really, driven by the realities of an officer's paycheque. Slightly better than the swill you drink to get through a working day, because you've got to do something special -- but only slightly.">>

<<SetSpeaker "Kim Kitsuragi">>
<<AddParagraph "The lieutenant takes a respectable sip of spirits and then carefully pours a portion onto the ice in front of him, an amber trail creeping towards the sunken carriage.">>

<<AddParagraph "After a moment of reflection, he passes you the bottle with clear reluctance.">>

<<NewTask "Libation for your MC">>

<<PassiveSkill "esprit de Corps" "Medium" "Success">>
<<AddParagraph "He's almost certain giving you this bottle is a very bad idea. Only respect for ancient cop tradition is forcing his hand. Don't make him regret this.">>
<<AddOption "Take the bottle" "Take the bottle">>
[[|Take the bottle]]


