<<SetSpeaker "SUNKEN MOTOR CARRIAGE">>
<<AddParagraph "You open your heart to the rusting carriage, taking in every detail to try and gleam some deeper understanding. Blue paint flaking off and into the sea. A canvas bit that... kept the rain out probably? Exposed cylinders and pipes and other winding metallic shapes that are where explosions happened you think?">>

<<PassiveSkill "Encyclopedia" "Challenging" "Failure">>
