:: ExpensiveCar [nobr] {"position":"1196,2856","size":"100,100"}
<<SetSpeaker "Kim Kitsuragi">>
<<AddParagraph "\The lieutenant nods solemnly. You know it took him many, many years of scrimping and saving to buy his own Coupris from the 57th.">>

<<PassiveSkill "esprit de Corps" "Godly" "Success">>
<<AddParagraph "Lieutenant Kim \“Kimball\” Kitsuragi’s face is a mask of perfect professionalism as he slides over his final payment to the requisitions officer. It’s only when he’s alone, running his hands over the sleek frame, lists of long planned modifications running through his mind, that he allows himself to smile.">>

<<SetSpeaker "Kim Kitsuragi">>
<<AddParagraph "\“Still, it worked out in the end. The precinct may be… unhappy with the loss of funds to the department, but with my Kineema they didn’t end up being down a vehicle.\”">>
