<<PassiveSkill "esprit de Corps" "Easy" "Success">>
<<AddParagraph "Just a few weeks ago, in a garage jammed into the side of an old silk mill, Jean Vicquemare lists the many terrible fates that he will personally inflict upon you if you so much as touch the wheel of another Coupris. Lieutenant Kitsuragi sits in the driver's seat, idly flipping through his notebook, seemingly nonplussed by the rising voices outside the motor carriage.">>

<<SetSpeaker "Kim Kitsuragi">>
<<AddParagraph "\"Don't look quite so glum detective. They'll forgive you eventually. In the end, people are more valuable than equipment, and what you do moving forward is more important than the mistakes in your past.\"">>

